21:50.331 --> 21:53.454
- Did he do his own fencing?
- Charlie!

21:53.534 --> 21:56.190
- Need you in the office.
- I'll be right there.

21:56.270 --> 21:58.011
Now, kiddo.

21:59.674 --> 22:01.529
Yep.

22:01.609 --> 22:04.215
Keep your head down, brother.

22:07.281 --> 22:09.136
You know why you're here?

22:09.216 --> 22:11.339
Let me take a crack at it.

22:11.419 --> 22:13.474
You're gonna say that I'm being difficult,

22:13.554 --> 22:15.710
