not only my own recovery

22:15.790 --> 22:17.963
but the recovery of those around me.

22:23.430 --> 22:27.221
Thank you, sir, for, uh,
taking time out of your very busy day.

22:27.301 --> 22:31.692
- Hello? Charlie?
- Dad.

22:31.772 --> 22:33.361
What do you think you're doing?

22:33.441 --> 22:35.263
