and already they want to throw you out.

22:38.979 --> 22:41.035
Sounds good.

22:41.115 --> 22:43.170
Go ahead, be glib.

22:43.250 --> 22:46.507
You think just 'cause you're 18,
everything will magically slide off you?

22:46.587 --> 22:48.242
