22:59.033 --> 23:01.722
Yeah, they wanted to press charges.

23:01.802 --> 23:04.792
But I pulled some strings
with a friend who knows the judge.

23:04.872 --> 23:08.362
And they said if you cooperate,
they'll let it go.

23:08.442 --> 23:10.364
But, hey, you're 18.

23:10.444 --> 23:12.633
You do whatever you want.

23:12.713 --> 23:16.937
Just know, if you don't comply,
you won't have to answer to me.

23:17.017 --> 23:19.440
You'll be facing possible jail time in Utah.

23:19.520 --> 23:21.329
It's your choice.

23:23.190 --> 23:25.079
Fine. You know what?

23:25.159 --> 23:27.448
I'll do the 30 days.

23:27.528 --> 23:30.651
And you can't just go through
the motions this time, Charlie.

23:30.731 --> 23:33.554
You have to complete the program
to their satisfaction.

23:33.634 --> 23:36.957
That could be longer than 30 days.

23:37.037 --> 23:38.859
Like, how long, Dad?

23:38.939 --> 23:42.352
Say, uh, till after the election?

23:43.411 --> 23:46.500
And if you leave or get expelled,

23:46.580 --> 23:48.890
