32:20.327 --> 32:22.316
Fine.

32:22.396 --> 32:23.684
Remember, less is more.

32:23.764 --> 32:25.619
- Hi.
- Can I help you?

32:25.699 --> 32:28.255
Yeah, uh, I'm just...
I'm looking for somebody.

32:28.335 --> 32:31.992
- Are you Charlie?
- Yeah.

32:32.072 --> 32:34.862
- Eva will see you at a meeting.
- No, I just wanted to say hi...

32:34.942 --> 32:36.649
Have a great day.

32:38.145 --> 32:40.367
Fat fucking whale!

32:40.447 --> 32:42.654
Hey!

32:43.917 --> 32:45.939
You know, you shouldn't talk
about whales like that,

32:46.019 --> 32:47.521
they're an endangered species.

32:48.789 --> 32:51.861
- Go around and wait for me, okay?
- Yeah?

32:58.966 --> 33:00.468
- Hey.
