33:03.103 --> 33:04.691
Who's that?

33:04.771 --> 33:07.761
Oh, that is my piece-of-shit best friend.

33:07.841 --> 33:10.412
Well, I thought I was your best friend.

33:11.912 --> 33:15.068
- You're such the comedian.
