33:15.148 --> 33:18.972
So, are you gonna break me out of here?

33:19.052 --> 33:21.475
Well, I thought, um,

33:21.555 --> 33:25.379
now that we're both out of in-patient,
and... and we have some free time,

33:25.459 --> 33:28.615
and, you know, uh, I was just
thinking that maybe we could...

33:28.695 --> 33:30.684
I think...

33:30.764 --> 33:32.386
Can I have your number?

33:34.901 --> 33:39.192
God, our first time on free soil
and you're asking for my number?

33:39.272 --> 33:41.428
Yeah.

33:41.508 --> 33:43.749
What, what's the matter?
You don't wanna give it to me?

33:44.811 --> 33:46.882
Not now.

33:58.025 --> 34:00.062
Do you have a pen?

34:01.328 --> 34:04.151
- Tapping that must've been a nice perk.
- I haven't.

34:04.231 --> 34:05.352
- What?
- Yeah.

34:05.432 --> 34:07.754
What are you talking about?
Are you just not making the moves?

34:07.834 --> 34:09.956
No, no, no, no, no. It's a rehab thing.

34:10.036 --> 34:12.926
- Like, we'd get tossed.
- Oh.

34:13.005 --> 34:15.795
- That's bullshit.
- Yeah, tell me about it.

34:15.876 --> 34:17.597
Men fuck each other in prison all the time.

34:17.677 --> 34:18.799
- What's the harm?
- Right?

34:18.879 --> 34:22.469
- Yeah.
