more freedom but more responsibility.

34:47.674 --> 34:50.429
You can come and go
as long as you sign in and out.

34:50.510 --> 34:54.333
- So, I can just leave?
- To the gas station or the market,

34:54.414 --> 34:57.738
but there's a 10:00 curfew,
and you'll be given random urine tests.

34:57.818 --> 35:00.407
- And if you fail...
- You'll keep it between us, right?

35:00.487 --> 35:02.042
Yeah?

35:02.122 --> 35:03.810
If you work hard and follow the rules,

35:03.890 --> 35:07.581
in about a month, you'll be eligible
for an overnight pass.

35:07.661 --> 35:10.217
Okay. Um...

35:10.297 --> 35:13.286
- there's still group, though, right?
- Every day at out-patient.

35:13.366 --> 35:15.455
And who attends these, uh, groups?

35:15.535 --> 35:17.057
What do you mean? Everybody.

35:17.137 --> 35:18.925
- Everybody?
- Yeah.

35:19.005 --> 35:21.228
- Eva's included in "everybody."
- I didn't mean that.

35:21.308 --> 35:23.363
You know, it's just good
to get different opinions.

35:23.443 --> 35:25.032
You can look but you can't touch.

35:25.112 --> 35:26.767
You'll be rooming with Jimmy.

35:26.847 --> 35:30.003
- Hey, man. What's up?
- Hey. Nothing much.

35:30.083 --> 35:33.440
- Remember, Charlie, wake up at 6:30.
- All right.

35:33.520 --> 35:35.509
Enjoy.

35:37.189 --> 35:39.012
Enjoy...

35:39.092 --> 35:42.349
So, uh, tell me.

35:42.429 --> 35:44.284
How shitty is this place?

35:44.364 --> 35:46.086
Compared to where we just were,
it's somewhat shitty.

35:46.166 --> 35:48.021
- Yeah?
- We got family group tomorrow,

35:48.101 --> 35:50.890
- which is gonna suck.
