this weekend.

35:54.407 --> 35:56.529
Oh, thank God I made it for that.

35:57.734 --> 36:00.367
- Charlie!
- Hey, Paul.

36:01.247 --> 36:03.036
You dirtbag.

36:03.116 --> 36:04.738
Hey, you're lucky they put you in with Jimmy.

36:04.818 --> 36:06.740
I had Chase.

36:06.820 --> 36:08.809
Chase? Oh, yeah, Chase.

36:08.889 --> 36:11.978
- Um, alcoholic.
- Experience, strength, and hope.

36:12.058 --> 36:14.848
