36:24.871 --> 36:26.326
Huh.

36:26.406 --> 36:28.795
Well, I guess his program
lost some of its rigor.

36:28.875 --> 36:31.164
I guess so.

36:31.244 --> 36:33.600
Now I'm stuck with Dylan.

36:33.680 --> 36:36.269
That guy jacks off right in front of me.

36:36.349 --> 36:37.537
